70cda7b239e54f65c455dafaf46a82550ea8b","tid":1223200,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:20:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"317d06d6fe027f12e6a513fa41e7e9805172799d","tid":1223200,"uid":161626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:48:19.000Z","msg":"[同我推晒佢] 力抗膠post 621行動討論整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242813</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"492e51d4ba0e75e5ea9aaf3e9e20220664e8169f","tid":1223200,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b17c96a592b991f16eaa5f6585e1cdeea77f14c2","tid":1223200,"uid":259928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"和理非請進(到底21號應唔應該衝)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243007</a>"},{"pid":"6679686a40d6ff6bba763c3361cc09ce330119cd","tid":1223200,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:46:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2388de448788eeafa3c5f8925b9a13e878566e26","tid":1223200,"uid":161626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:47:18.000Z","msg":"[同我推晒佢] 力抗膠post 621行動討論整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242813</a><br />\n<br />\n再玩膠，我地就會輸，唔好再俾膠post分散我地嘅注意力，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我推晒下面啲post上熱門！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">催淚彈、胡椒噴霧</span></span><br />\n發夢夢到幾個德國朋友教我點處理催淚彈 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1218344/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1218344/page/1</a><br />\n[Gear撚] 催淚彈對防指南 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1</a><br />\n［學術］中咗催淚彈同胡椒噴霧解決方法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1</a><br />\n[廣傳][長文]長期革命，每個人都要準備對抗催淚彈/胡椒噴磅必須用品 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">裝備</span></span><br />\n&lt;抗爭手冊&gt; <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2</a><br />\n振興香港消費！全城戶外運動裝備及須知 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1</a><br />\n知己知彼 百戰百勝圖解香港警察裝備 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1</a><br />\n最近有個新喪屍GAME IDEA <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1</a><br />\n[突發] 621 雙方陣營裝備分析 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1</a><br />\n[魔防的重要性］所有人都要有足夠魔防 N95同泳鏡係最低要求 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1</a><br />\n星期五嘅野餐行動 請現在立即做兩樣野 購買裝備 同 加強文宣 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241812/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241812/page/1</a><br />\n[突發]新假期繼野餐之後又癡咗線 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242741/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242741/page/1</a><br />\n緊急！邊度可以買魔防裝 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242751/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242751/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">盾牌</span></span><br />\n[歷史台][積極備盾] 盾牌陣不是亂擺一通的 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241049/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241049/page/1</a><br />\n廉價盾牌材料 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1200677/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1200677/page/1</a><br />\n對付警犬最強盾牌buff <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216654/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216654/page/1</a><br />\n得黑警有盾牌？我都有！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1225742/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1225742/page/1</a><br />\n盾牌警棍頭盔：反政府示威者裝備不輸警察 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240310/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240310/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">物資</span></span><br />\n作為一個物資站站長，我想同大家道個歉 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1222678/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1222678/page/1</a><br />\n野餐物資／通訊檢討小組（重開）<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">鐵馬</span></span><br />\n鐵馬一定要放最前！鐵馬一定要有流動性！ <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1238720/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1238720/page/1</a><br />\n[人人都要識] 倒三角扎鐵馬 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240447/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240447/page/1</a><br />\n鐵馬最新安置法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216269/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">地形</span></span><br />\n圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">IT</span></span><br />\n[正式上架] 手機抗警犬 用相機Scan數字即出黑警資料 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241300/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"dcf998cfb6e01425b7620619b2ef86dc8d457f82","tid":1223200,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8127bd41d762574ecc6967f28d16ba43ea6678f","tid":1223200,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"633dca5cedad4d2b7d89440192fc661f4fffc812","tid":1223200,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:59:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"066b534f56f81646e5e8713af7f39cc33924b280","tid":1223200,"uid":206021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:01:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d8362da9b471d431df10ce6f9856a0f23e5de42a","tid":1223200,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:06:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d2c5292f542f618579fa12d9a7c71a9211b1477","tid":1223200,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:38:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[同我推晒佢] 力抗膠post 621行動討論整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242813</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"f89bae2017a05407548c8f2dd7c8395d18b4635a","tid":1223200,"uid":48044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:58:42.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd5e500e947aa4231549763fa400f577bde8ebc","tid":1223200,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2aade7a07f804500d1810f038d3888d0e56c5456","tid":1223200,"uid":172166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:16:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"610801305cff6f3f2a5af9ff3935aafe92d9cdbe","tid":1223200,"uid":265451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"發夢諗到一啲方法對付克驚，唔知以下呢啲方法有冇幫助呢？<br />\n<br />\n1:將梘液搽落自己件衫/身上，提高俾犬捉住時掙脫嘅機會率。<br />\n<br />\n2:一人準備一把扇，放催淚煙嗰陣可以一齊撥走佢。<br />\n<br />\n3:多帶備消毒酒精/濕紙巾甚至係安美露、洗手液，中左催淚煙/胡椒水嗰陣可以用裡面嘅酒精洗走裡面溶於醇嘅化學物質。"},{"pid":"1e2d0a2db49f0adc0c79e738640f47761ef18847","tid":1223200,"uid":161626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:18:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df60d86a57af864d76a5685f2d3f04a7a522425b","tid":1223200,"uid":53465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:51:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99bb44dedd100ce6dfdd4b27bf5ef8f5cd482f1c","tid":1223200,"uid":196087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"唔戴con唔得，唯有笠實啲個眼罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cae6e0d3341c4ac475bb6a1aae10d711117086","tid":1223200,"uid":181393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:04:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3e45e82dcb1d605fd412cc1fa77002b9296c62d8","tid":1223200,"uid":98672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50305130117b4ef821539f93d866a48b74603256","tid":1223200,"uid":98672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998919733fb09137ad4423f379cbe8cc8d0f2df2","tid":1223200,"uid":255816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0b5bbaabeb1cf5d104f68d54f6e1cf01b13f1ed","tid":1223200,"uid":38131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:29:02.000Z","msg":"發夢如果食正催淚彈<br />\n會嚴重呼吸困難<br />\n喉嚨好似俾火燒<br />\n眼水不斷漂<br />\n冇裝備係入面一定頂唔住<br />\n但離開左大概5分鐘就完全冇事<br />\n個人夢境經驗<br />\n<br />\n但啲水劑就麻煩好多<br />\nHi到會feel到少少灼熱感<br />\n再過一陣好似俾火燒緊咁<br />\n但如果死頂可以頂到<br />\n不過會last好耐<br />\n起碼1個鐘"},{"pid":"c2e087817143db1b78935cb9266178ccbe55c697","tid":1223200,"uid":69177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22eb73e422e50e96f34113fa74ae00d73a0a030","tid":1223200,"uid":83785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17868398f52a239800ead042ca68c7bc27041545","tid":1223200,"uid":82128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec72cef8d29e17e369c381c7c4fdbdf2368845cf","tid":1223200,"uid":264994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d1b543dd7a5f7a48ebd896495804a9bee35dbf5","tid":1223200,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:42:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2191acd64017a4201c600772caf846fa2a3f2de4","tid":1223200,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:44:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n人人化身補師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c67b92ef36b80d788cb17eb760eaca9f406533b","tid":1223200,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"84e86a609655232831793a49dfcac6ad85819ef0","tid":1223200,"uid":155180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c4250b196e45ce46d1bdc23648b564ec649650","tid":1223200,"uid":166117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T14:45:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b33e575e07056ed5ec2a3842c6c9130eb598524e","tid":1223200,"uid":161436,"lik